'''布萊森·德尚布'''（{{lang-en|'''Bryson James Aldrich DeChambeau'''}}，{{bd|1993年|9月16日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位職業[[高爾夫球|高爾夫球]]手。在2015年，他成為歷史上第五位在同年獲得NCAA一級錦標賽和美國業餘高爾夫錦標賽冠軍的球手<ref name=usamglfch>{{cite news |last=Lavner |first=Ryan |title=DeChambeau tops Bard, 7 and 6, in U.S. Am final |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/ryan-lavner/dechambeau-tops-bard-7-and-6-us-am-final/ |work=Golf Channel |date=2015-08-23 |access-date=2016-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826022001/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/ryan-lavner/dechambeau-tops-bard-7-and-6-us-am-final/ |archive-date=2015-08-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2020年，他贏得[[美國高爾夫公開賽|美國高爾夫公開賽]]冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pgatour.com/news/2020/09/20/bryson-dechambeau-cruises-to-us-open-title-wins-by-six-shots-winged-foot.html|script-title=en:DeChambeau cruises to U.S. Open title|accessdate=2020-09-21|publisher={{lang|en|PGA tour}}|language=en|deadurl=no|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004061236/https://www.pgatour.com/news/2020/09/20/bryson-dechambeau-cruises-to-us-open-title-wins-by-six-shots-winged-foot.html}}</ref>。

==業餘生涯==
德尚布出生在加州[[莫德斯托_(加利福尼亞州)|莫德斯托]]，後在7歲時搬家到位於[[弗雷斯諾|弗雷斯諾]]東北的[[克洛維斯_(加利福尼亞州)|克洛維斯]]。他曾就讀於{{link-en|克洛維斯東高中|Clovis East High School}}，並在2010年16歲時贏得加利福尼亞州少年錦標賽冠軍。2012年，他從高中畢業，並因獲得體育獎學金而就讀[[得克薩斯州|得克薩斯州]][[達拉斯|達拉斯]]的[[南方卫理公会大学|南方卫理公会大学]]，主攻[[物理學|物理學]]。

2015年6月，他成為首位獲得{{link-en|NCAA男子高爾夫一級錦標賽|NCAA Division I Men's Golf Championships}}冠軍的南方衛理會大學學生。在決賽中他四輪總桿數為280（−8），一一桿優勢獲勝<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://archive.golfweek.com/news/2015/jun/01/ncaa-golf-college-men-smu-bryson-dechambeau-medal/ |title=Positive attitude helps SMU's Bryson DeChambeau to NCAA individual title |last=Romine |first=Brentley |date=2015-06-02 |magazine=Golfweek |access-date=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611221825/http://archive.golfweek.com/news/2015/jun/01/ncaa-golf-college-men-smu-bryson-dechambeau-medal/ |archive-date=2016-06-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。德尚布還在八月獲得了美國業餘賽冠軍，成為繼[[傑克·尼克勞斯|傑克·尼克勞斯]]（1961）、[[菲爾·米克森|菲爾·米克森]]（1990）、[[老虎伍茲|老虎伍茲]]（1996）、[[瑞安·摩爾|瑞安·摩爾]]（2004）之後第五個達成這一成績的選手<ref name=usamglfch/>。

德尚布在2015年6月以業餘球手的身份參加了[[聯邦快遞聖裘德經典賽|聯邦快遞聖裘德經典賽]]，這是他首次出場[[PGA巡迴賽|PGA巡迴賽]]，並獲得第45名的成績。他參加了{{link-en|2015年美國高爾夫公開賽|2015 U.S. Open (golf)}}，這是他首次參加[[四大賽|四大賽]]，但以四桿差距未能晉級<ref name=espnfifcb>{{cite news |url=http://espn.go.com/golf/leaderboard?tournamentId=2249 |work=ESPN |title=U.S. Open leaderboard |date=2015-06-20 |accessdate=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2016-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160726061851/http://espn.go.com/golf/leaderboard?tournamentId=2249 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在南方卫理公会大学的體育部門被禁止參加NCAA賽事之後，德尚布未能在2016衛冕他的NCAA冠軍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/ncaa-bans-smu-postseason-play-violations/ |title=SMU gets postseason ban; DeChambeau can't defend |work=Golf Channel |date=2015-09-29 |first=Ryan |last=Lavner |access-date=2017-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001165433/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/ncaa-bans-smu-postseason-play-violations |archive-date=2015-10-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他決定在成為職業球手之前放棄他在大學的最後一個賽季<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-postpone-senior-year-focus-masters/ |title=DeChambeau to delay sr. year, focus on Masters |work=Golf Channel |first=Ryan |last=Lavner |date=2015-10-13 |access-date=2017-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016232323/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-postpone-senior-year-focus-masters |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在2015年{{link-en|澳大利亞大師賽|Australian Masters}}上，德尚布和[[約翰·薩登|約翰·薩登]]、安德魯·伊文斯獲得並列亞軍<ref name=swausmasts>{{cite news |url=http://www.pgatour.com/news/2015/11/22/peter-senior-wins-australian-masters-age-56.html |publisher=PGA Tour |agency=Associated Press |title=Senior wins Australian Masters at age 56 |date=2015-11-22 |accessdate=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113150544/http://www.pgatour.com/news/2015/11/22/peter-senior-wins-australian-masters-age-56.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年，他以業餘球手身份參加{{link-en|2016年美國大師賽|2016 Masters Tournament}}，獲得並列第21位<ref name=espnmstsxtn>{{cite news |url=http://espn.go.com/golf/leaderboard?tournamentId=2493 |work=ESPN |title=Masters leaderboard |date=2016-04-10 |accessdate=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2016-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731005035/http://espn.go.com/golf/leaderboard?tournamentId=2493 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
在2016年4月中旬的大師賽之後，德尚布很快成為職業選手，並和Cobra-Puma高爾夫簽訂了一份長期契約<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.bunkered.co.uk/golf-news/bryson-dechambeaus-big-signing |title=Bryson DeChambeau's Big signing |date=2016-04-13 |magazine=bunkered |first=Martin |last=Inglis |access-date=2017-07-19 |archive-date=2016-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161205205245/http://www.bunkered.co.uk/golf-news/bryson-dechambeaus-big-signing |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他參加的首個賽事是[[傳承盃高球賽|傳承盃高球賽]]，成績是並列第四名，並獲得259,000美元的獎金<ref>{{cite news |last=Lavner |first=Ryan |title=DeChambeau earns low am at Masters; pro debut looms |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-earns-low-am-masters-pro-debut-looms/ |work=Golf Channel |date=2016-04-10 |accessdate=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412044129/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-earns-low-am-masters-pro-debut-looms/ |archive-date=2016-04-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/sports/golf/article71276332.html |title=On Grand Strand Golf: Day, DeChambeau headline RBC Heritage field |publisher=MyrtleBeachOnline |date=2016-04-11 |first=Alan |last=Blondin |accessdate=2017-07-19 |archive-date=2016-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423012248/http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/sports/golf/article71276332.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。決定成為職業球手意味德尚布無法直接參加{{link-en|2016年美國高爾夫公開賽|2016 U.S. Open (golf)}}和{{link-en|2016年英國高爾夫公開賽|2016 Open Championship}}。他獲得了美國公開賽的參賽權，排名並列第15位並獲得152,000美元獎金<ref name=espnsxtoa>{{cite news |url=http://espn.go.com/golf/leaderboard?tournamentId=2501 |work=ESPN |title=U.S. Open leaderboard |date=2016-06-17 |accessdate=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2016-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723133651/http://espn.go.com/golf/leaderboard?tournamentId=2501 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[男子高爾夫世界排名|男子高爾夫世界排名]]也提高到148位。

雖然開局強勁，但德尚布未能獲得足夠積分以參加PGA巡迴賽參賽權，但可以參加{{link-en|Web.com巡迴賽總決賽|Web.com Tour Finals}}。他在{{link-en|DAP冠軍賽|DAP Championship}}獲得了自己的首頁職業賽事冠軍，使得他獲得{{link-en|2017年PGA巡迴賽|2017 PGA Tour}}參賽權<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-clinches-tour-card-finals-win/ |title=DeChambeau clinches Tour card with Web.com win |work=Golf Channel |first=Will |last=Gray |date=2016-09-11 |access-date=2017-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329054145/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-clinches-tour-card-finals-win/ |archive-date=2017-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.pgatour.com/news/2017/16-17-eligibility-ranking.html |title=2016-17 PGA Tour Eligibility Ranking |publisher=PGA Tour |access-date=2017-03-28 |archive-date=2017-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331043242/http://www.pgatour.com/news/2017/16-17-eligibility-ranking.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年7月16日，德尚布獲得[[約翰·迪爾精英賽|約翰·迪爾精英賽]]冠軍，這是他的首個PGA巡迴賽冠軍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-wins-john-deere-qualifies-open/ |title=Deere win propels DeChambeau to Open at Birkdale |publisher=NBC GOLF |access-date=2017-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718220230/http://www.golfchannel.com/news/golf-central-blog/dechambeau-wins-john-deere-qualifies-open |archive-date=2017-07-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==獨特球具==
有別於普通{{le|鐵桿|Iron (golf)}}長度遞減的設計，德尚布所有的鐵桿長度相同<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.golfdigestweb.com.tw/article/3375|title=優勝者的袋中武器：布萊森‧迪尚博，2020美國公開賽|publisher=[[高爾夫文摘|高爾夫文摘]]|date=2020-09-21|access-date=2021-08-06|archive-date=2021-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806035431/https://www.golfdigestweb.com.tw/article/3375|dead-url=no}}</ref>，均是{{convert|37.5|in|m|3}}，且著地角和反彈角的角度也相同，只有桿面傾角不同<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Inglis |first=Martin |title=18 things you ought to know about Bryson DeChambeau |url=http://www.bunkered.co.uk/golf-news/18-things-you-ought-to-know-about-bryson-dechambeau |magazine=bunkered |date=2016-01-21 |access-date=2017-07-19 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729131716/http://www.bunkered.co.uk/golf-news/18-things-you-ought-to-know-about-bryson-dechambeau |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德尚布為使用此設計的先軀，[[眼鏡蛇高爾夫|眼鏡蛇高爾夫]]及後於2017年將One Length球桿推出市面。另外德尚布還在揮桿時保持球具處在同一平面，並且不在揮桿時轉動手腕<ref>{{cite news |last=Kerr-Dineen |first=Luke |title=How Bryson DeChambeau's fascinating swing could revolutionize golf |url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/04/how-bryson-dechambeaus-fascinating-swing-could-revolutionize-golf |newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=2016-04-12 |accessdate=2017-07-19 |archive-date=2017-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719101003/http://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/04/how-bryson-dechambeaus-fascinating-swing-could-revolutionize-golf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，應他教練的建議，德尚布轉用了比普通球桿握把部分粗上幾倍的JumboMax Grips，將球桿握在掌心之中，這樣更加有利於他獨特揮桿姿勢的發揮<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/golf/2018/06/25/bryson-dechambeau-faces-investigation-using-protractor/ |title=Bryson DeChambeau faces investigation for using a protractor |newspaper=The Telegraph |first=James |last=Corrigan |date=June 25, 2018 |access-date=September 22, 2020 |archive-date=2021-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609111753/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/golf/2018/06/25/bryson-dechambeau-faces-investigation-using-protractor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

